1.title: Episode #1.1

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

1.plot: As Vibhuthi is busy dreaming about a romantic moment with his neighbor Angoori, his wife sees him enjoying his sleep and assumes that he is dreaming about her. Later, Vibhuthi is forced to go out of the house to buy some milk and Vibhuthi is mesmerized by Angoori's beautiful voice. He is later introduced to Manmohan Tiwari's younger brother Laddoo who has the power to hear what one says in his mind. Meanwhile, Manmohan Tiwari wakes up and learns that there is no water in his house. Manmohan decides to go to Vibuthi's house to have his bath and decides to use this time...

552.title: Badtameez Damad

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

552.plot: Anita is happy that her uncle has called her up and she reminds him that her uncle was the one, who had helped her study abroad. Later, Anita is disappointed upon learning that the boy, whom Anita's uncle wanted her to marry now has almost fifty bank branches that he is managing. Further, when Anita's uncle questions Anita about how Vibhuti is, Anita lies that Vibhuti is the CEO of a multinational company. Immediately, Anita's uncle wishes to meet Vibhuti and Anita is left with no other option but to force Vibhuti to pretend like a CEO of a multinational company.

553.title: Badtameez Damad - Part 2

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

553.plot: Anita's uncle believes that Vibhuti is Anita's brother-in-law. Later, Anita's uncle informs them that Vibhuti's misbehavior towards him has made him come up with the decision to get his undisciplined daughter to marry Vibhuti. Anita and Vibhuti are instantly shocked. They share the news with Manmohan and Angoori and Manmohan is unable to control his laughter. After thinking of a plan for a while to get out of their current situation, Angoori decides to lie to Anita's uncle about Vibhuti having a girlfriend. Finally, it is decided that Angoori will pretend to be ...

554.title: Badtameez Damad - Part 3

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

554.plot: Anita's uncle decides to get the 'roka' done for Vibhuti as he wants his daughter, Pinki to marry Vibhuti. In order to avoid the 'roka', Angoori, who is pretending to be Vibhuti's girlfriend, claims that she is pregnant with Vibhuti's child. Saxena witnesses everything and unaware of the drama unfolding, he enters the house and begins beating up Vibhuti. Later, Anita's uncle decides to get both Pinki and Angoori married to Vibhuti. That night, Manmohan gets angry with Angoori for claiming to be pregnant with Vibhuti's child. However, Anita calms him down and they all ...

555.title: Kiraayedaar

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

555.plot: Anita invites a journalist from Kanpur Express to put an advertisement about putting their hall area on rent. Vibhuti is not comfortable with the idea, but has no choice other than accepting Anita's preposition about the same. Manmohan overhears this discussion and is excited as he might get a chance to live with Anita . To make his plan work he tries to pick a fight with Angoori so that he will have a genuine reason to stay as a tenant in Anita's house. Stay tuned to know whether Manmohan's plan will work or not.

556.title: Kiraayedaar Part2

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

556.plot: Angoori is worried about Manmohan's whereabouts and just then, Vibhuti informs her that Manmohan is staying in his house as a tenant. Vibhuti tries to brainwash Angoori against Manmohan but just then, Manmohan's mother reaches the scene and begins shouting at Vibhuti. Meanwhile, Anita slips on the floor of the hall and she gets furious seeing that Manmohan has kept all his clothes in the hall for drying and has ended up wetting the floor. Angoori remembers Manmohan during the night and just then, Manmohan arrives. The two of them share a romantic moment and Angoori ...

557.title: Bhoot ka Jhooth

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

557.plot: Anita is surprised when she gets a call from her uncle asking her for a sum of five lakh rupees. She asks Vibhuti to arrange the amount anyhow and prove his capabilities. Vibhuti decides to arrange for the money by asking Prem or Manmohan to lend him the sum but Anita refuses to borrow any money. Anita believes that they will have to leave the house and shift back to the old house in Kanpur. Vibhuti makes up his mind not to leave the house as he will have to leave Angoori Bhabi forever. Watch Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hain to know what solution will Vibhuti come up with.

558.title: Bhoot ka Jhooth Part2

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

558.plot: The entire neighborhood including Manmohan and Angoori attend the last rites of Vibhuti as they believe that he is dead. Vibhuti, on the other hand, sits next to Anita, wearing a disguise of an old man. All close friends of Vibhuti speak about him as they miss him and Vibhuti, who is wearing a disguise, is surprised listening to what everyone thinks of him. Later, Angoori stands up to speak about Vibhuti and she is upset that Vibhuti had to die as a jobless man. Vibhuti pretends to be his own uncle and expresses his anger towards the others for speaking ill of him ...

559.title: Bhoot ka Jhooth - Part3

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

559.plot: Manmohan believes that he did not find any spark of sadness on Anita's face in spite the fact that her husband is dead. Anita tries to explain that she is a brave woman and is trying to move ahead. Later, Vibhuti appears before Angoori and believing that he is Vibhuti's ghost, Angoori communicates with him. Later, Manmohan questions Angoori as to whom she was talking to. Angoori informs Manmohan that she had been speaking to Vibhuti's ghost and listening to her, Manmohan starts to get scared. Later, Manmohan sees Anita romancing Vibhuti and Manmohan believes that ...

560.title: Bhoot ka Jhooth - Part4

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

560.plot: Manmohan is scared to see Vibhuti's ghost standing before him. Vibhuti joins Manmohan and gulps down a few shots of alcohol. After getting drunk, Vibhuti leaves. Later, Malkhan and Tika reach the place and learn from Manmohan that he had just had drinks with Vibhuti's ghost. Later, Malkhan, Tika and Happu discuss about the feast that is to take place after few days of Vibhuti's death.

561.title: Anita bani Chef

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

561.plot: Anita is upset with Vibhuti as he had been praising the food prepared by Angoori and stating that the food prepared by her is the best in the entire town. Anita makes up her mind to prove that she can cook and she decides to invite Angoori and Manmohan for lunch. Next day, Manmohan sees Anita cooking and he expresses his joy watching Anita cook. Later, Happu arrives and starts expressing his excitement upon watching Anita cook. Happu then wishes to be a part of the lunch and Anita invites Happu too.

562.title: Kunwari Angoori

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

562.plot: Vibhuti picks up a rose from the road and offers it to Anita, claiming that the rose is an expensive one from the land of Kashmir. Just when Anita is impressed, Manmohan arrives and shows Anita a video in which Vibhuti is seen picking up the rose from the road. Later, Anita and Vibhuti visit Angoori and Manmohan's house. Just as the four of them are busy in a discussion, the pundit, who had gotten Angoori and Manmohan married, arrives. He informs that Manmohan and Angoori are technically not married as the the prayers being recited by him were not that of marriage.

563.title: Kunwari Angoori - Part 2

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

563.plot: Manmohan and Happu reach Gulfam Kali's place to take part in the bachelor's party organized by Manmohan on Vibhuti's insistence. However, Vibhuti himself seems to be missing from the bachelor's party. While, Gulfam Kali appears before Happu and Manmohan, all set to entertain them, Anita and Angoori discuss about the saree that she will be wearing for her marriage. Later, Vibhuti watches the television in front of Anita and Angoori and both the ladies are shocked when they watch Happu and Manmohan enjoying Gulfam Kali's dance.

564.title: Kunwari Angoori - Part 3

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

564.plot: Vibhuti and Pelu start gambling on the middle of the road. Inspector Happu reaches the scene and tries to teach Vibhuti the laws of the area but both Vibhuti and Pelu leave the scene after handing over the cards to Manmohan and Happu. Meanwhile, Anita and Angoori still cannot believe the news about Manmohan being with Gulfam Kali. Later, Vibhuti reaches Angoori's home and wishes to watch the news. Angoori is shocked when she sees the news reporter reporting about Manmohan and Happu gambling in the middle of the road.

565.title: Mantri se lagaav, Vibhuti ke badhe bhaav

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

565.plot: Manmohan is upset that his business is shut at the moment. Meanwhile, Happu finds himself in trouble after he has been accused of taking a bribe. As Happu discusses his matter with Malkhan and Tika, a minister reaches the scene, parks his car and goes straight to Vibhuti's house. Happu, Malkhan and Tika are certain that the Minister will have no work with a useless man like Vibhuti but end up surprised when the Minister asks for Vibhuti. As they all wait outside the house now joined by Anita, inside the house, the Minister beats up Vibhuti, accusing him of having an ...

566.title: Mantri se lagaav, Vibhuti ke badhe bhaav - Part 2

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

566.plot: Believing that Vibhuti is friends with the minister, Malkhan, Tika and Happu plead with him to solve their problems. Next day, Vibhuti meets the minister's wife with all the problems and she agrees to solve all of the problems but asks Vibhuti to feed her the 'pani puri' first. Vibhuti obliges, unaware that he is being watched by the minister and his wife, Anita. Later, Manmohan, Happu, Malkhan and Tika reach Vibhuti's house with gifts but they are shocked when Anita enters the house, informing all of them that Vibhuti is having an affair with the minister's wife.

567.title: Blackmail ka khel

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

567.plot: Manmohan and Vibhuti narrate stories in order to insult each other. Just then, Happu arrives and tell them about a death in the neighborhood and explains that the person had died due to electric shock. That night, Anita warns Vibhuti against having any affair with any woman. Just then, Vibhuti gets a call but Vibhuti gets no reply to his constant 'hellos'. Anita assumes that a girl had called up Vibhuti.

568.title: Blackmail ka khel - Part 2

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

568.plot: Vibhuti meets Angoori and claims that his senses and body parts are in not coordination with each other. He goes on to blow kisses at Angoori but apologizes to her by saying that he has no control of his lips or even what he is speaking. Later, Vibhuti reaches home and feels insulted as Anita is speaking on the phone with her friend, who has just received a surprise gift from her husband. Moments later, the doorbell rings and Anita goes to open the door.

569.title: Blackmail ka khel - Part 3

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

569.plot: Vibhuti meets Angoori, apologizing to her for his behavior against Manmohan. He explains that he has no control over the actions of his body parts. He winks at her and even ends up saying 'I Love You' to her but instantly apologizes for the actions of his body parts. Later, Manmohan meets inspector Happu and pleads with him to write a report as he wants to file a complaint against Vibhuti, who had beaten him up with slippers. However, Happu refuses to turn this minor matter into a police case.

572.title: Chandi ki Cycle Sone ka Scooter

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

572.plot: Unable to bear the heat, as Manmohan leaves his room, he sees Anita walking haphazardly towards her house. Manmohan follows her and sees her falling unconscious on the sofa. As Manmohan begins to scream, Vibhuti arrives and does not seem much bothered and explains that it is usual for Anita to behave this way during the summers. Later, Anita expresses her disappointment towards Vibhuti for failing to provide her with the comfort of a vehicle. Later, Vibhuti gets a cycle for Anita and takes her on a ride, leaving Manmohan jealous. Manmohan instantly makes up his mind ...

573.title: Chandi ki Cycle Sone ka Scooter - Part 2

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

573.plot: Vibhuti beats up Saxena, who punctured his cycle. He feels bad as he loses the opportunity take Angoori on a ride. Meanwhile, Manmohan buys a brand new scooter and Malkhan and Tika assume that the scooter is for them. When Manmohan drives away with the scooter, Malkhan and Tika feel bad. By now, Vibhuti reaches Angoori with cycle and offers her a ride. But, once again, his dreams are shattered as Manmohan arrives on his scooter and takes Angoori away. Just then, Anita arrives after suffering from another sun stroke.

574.title: Chandi ki Cycle Sone ka Scooter - Part 3

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

574.plot: Manmohan is angry that Vibhuti gets to take Anita on a ride on his bicycle so he punctures the tyre of Vibhuti's cycle. Later, when Vibhuti and Anita are about to leave their home, they notice the punctured cycle and Vibhuti immediately leaves to fix it. Manmohan takes advantage of the situation and offers ride to Anita on his scooter but just then, a member of Anita's grooming classes arrives and takes Anita along with him. Manmohan gets furious but to make matters only worse, Happu hits him with his scooter, causing Manmohan to break his leg.

575.title: Vibhu Tiwari pe Majnu squad

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

575.plot: Vibhuti meets Angoori in the morning and faces insult from her when she innocently speaks about his joblessness. Moments later, Manmohan and Anita join them after completing their jogging session. Happu arrives on a rickshaw and makes an announcement that he is in-charge of the 'Romeo Squad' that will be protecting women against eve teasers and others creating trouble for women.

576.title: Vibhu Tiwari pe Majnu squad - Part 2

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

576.plot: Saxena wishes to get arrested by Happu, so that he can be beaten up but Happu informs him that law is not the same for those, who are mentally ill. Later, Happu begins beating the commissioner, assuming that he is openly romancing with a girl. While Happu begins to apologize to the commissioner, he is allowed to leave after a stern warning. Later, Happu brings Vibhuti home, who was arrested for feeding street food to his wife. Meanwhile, Angoori and Manmohan get romantic but are interrupted by Happu, who arrests Manmohan for getting romantic with his wife. Later, ...

577.title: Vibhu par sawaar mistry banane ka khumaar

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

577.plot: Laddu's 'masterji' beats up Manmohan with a stick as he talks loudly on the phone while he (master) is teaching Laddu. Afterward, Manmohan sees a portion of the wall in his house being damaged because of water. He tells Angoori about the same and says that he will look for a worker to fix this. Meanwhile, Vibhuti uses up the money meant for the phone bill to buy an expensive pair of goggles for himself and gets scolded by Anu.

578.title: Vibhu par sawaar mistry banane ka khumaar - Part 2

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

578.plot: Vibhuti reaches Manmohan's house late at night and asks him for money as he says that he has to buy stuff for renovation of their house. Manmohan gets irritated but gives Vibhuti money as Angoori tells him too. The next day, Manmohan gets angry as he sees Angoori giving food to Vibhuti, Malkan and Teeka and goes to complain to Anita about it. When Anita comes to check on Vibhuti with Manmohan, she sees her working and gets angry on Manmohan instead as he got her late to work. Till how long will Vibhuti continue with his drama of trying to fix the damping in the wall ...

585.plot: Gulfam Kali's soon to be father-in-law takes aim at the apple on Tika's head and prepares to shoot. Later, the situation is diverted when Anita and Angoori wish to get married to Manmohan and Vibhuti as they claim that they have fallen in love with the dacoits.

587.title: Episode #1.587

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

587.plot: Manmohan scolds Angoori, who is singing and asks her to stay silent. Angoori begins to cry and makes up her mind to never sing for him even if he asks her to. Meanwhile, Anita taunts Vibhuti as she points out to his joblessness. Next morning, Vibhuti is surprised when he does not hear Angoori singing. He later learns that Manmohan has ordered her not to sing and this infuriates Vibhuti.

588.title: Episode #1.588

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

588.plot: Manmohan, who is suffering from the hearing problem, enters Anita's house and shocks her when he does not understand her words and instead misunderstands everything that she says to him. Just then, Anita gets a call from her friend Rajwati who informs her that she will be in India along with her husband and the two of them will be meeting her. Meanwhile, Vibhuti gets into an outfit meant for musicians and he gets Malkhan, Tika, Saxena and Tillu to wear a similar outfit. As they all get ready with musical instruments, Vibhuti begins singing and Angoori joins him.

589.title: Episode #1.589

episode of.title: Bhabi Ji Ghar Par Hai (TV Series 2015– )

589.plot: Vibhuti, who is now heading the band, gets furious with Happu as he refers to him as a jobless person. Vibhuti reverts by saying that Happu is the real jobless person as he is not doing his duty in spite of having a job in hand. Moments later, the 'sanskari' teacher arrives and requests the band's presence for ceremony that is to be held the next day. Next morning, Angoori informs Anita that Manmohan had ordered her to stop singing and in order to prove herself, she was forced to join Vibhuti's band as the lead singer.
